==古生物学==
根据其近亲[[奇翼龙|奇翼龙]]，它可能拥有某种膜翅以允许滑翔，但是其翅膀上似乎缺少[[飞羽|飞羽]]。<ref name="zhangnature2008"/><ref>Cau, A (2012), [http://theropoda.blogspot.pt/2012/07/il-ritorno-del-paraviano-pterosauro.html Il ritorno del paraviano pterosauro-mimo?] {{Wayback|url=http://theropoda.blogspot.pt/2012/07/il-ritorno-del-paraviano-pterosauro.html |date=20170827045741 }}, Theropoda, July 2012</ref>
